      <T n="text">0xD3F53B7F<!--String: "You may now <b><font color='#199C2C'>Adopt an existing Sim</font></b> as long as your Sim is of an older age bracket!\n\nThis allows you to adopt <b><font color='#199C2C'>Children, Teens, Young Adults and Adults</font></b>. Adopting a Sim is a great way to enlarge your Household or even find an Heir for your Dynasty!\n\nTo do so, the Sim you wish to Adopt <b><font color='#199C2C'>must have only 1 other parent or no parents</font></b>. Select the Sim you want to Adopt, then the Relationship interaction category, then Change Relationship.\n\nYou may also have your Sim <b><font color='#199C2C'>Ask to be Adopted</font></b> by another Sim! This interaction is available in the Relationship category as well, and can be done by a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Teen, Young Adult or Adult</font></b> towards an older Sim they're close to."--></T>
